Installing an IBM MQ server 
===========================
download the MQ trials version
unzip and untar using ---
As root,run the mqlicense.sh script. If you want to view a text-only version of the license, which can be read by a screen reader, type the following message:
./mqlicense.sh -text_only


install in default location 
rpm -ivh MQSeriesRuntime-*.rpm MQSeriesServer-*.rpm

installing in custom location 
rpm --prefix /opt/customLocation -ivh MQSeriesRuntime-*.rpm
MQSeriesServer-*.rpm

-- customlocaiton is the location of installation 


